articles.title: Thousands gather at Bondi Beach to mourn victims of antisemitic attack - AP News
articles.description: Thousands of mourners have gathered at Sydney’s Bondi Beach to mark a week since two gunmen targeted a Jewish festival, killing 15 people. The attack has spurred Australian governments to act against antisemitism and tighten gun controls. Prime Minister Antho…
